Swiss Stocks Decline, Erasing Earlier Gains; Holcim Leads Drop

-- B y   C o r i n n e   G r e t l e r
-- 
2011-09-21T12:20:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/swiss-stocks-erase-gains-smi-is-little-changed-in-zurich.html
Swiss stocks fell, erasing earlier
gains, as  Holcim Ltd. (HOLN)  and  Transocean Ltd. (RIG)  declined.  The  Swiss Market Index (SMI)  dropped 0.3 percent to 5,456.03 at
2:19 p.m. in Zurich, having earlier risen as much as 0.8
percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Corinne Gretler in Zurich at 
